statusd
-------

statusd - a lightweight status daemon, built for my own use.
Configurable using the FORMAT string in statusd.c:

	%B - bluetooth status (Bluez)
	%b - battery icon & percent (uses /sys/class/power_supply)
	%d - day in year, ex. '16 Nov'
	%t - current 24h time, ex. '15:22'
	%n - network icon (uses DBus + NetworkManager)
	%v - volume muted/not-muted icon (pamixer)
